title: GIVE ME AN S

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: So why no s riot??? ANSWER ME. WHERE DID I GO WRONG???!!!! I literally had more kills then the entire enemy team and got an A

replies.body:
CS. 106 in a 35 min game is low, and Fizz being an assassin (with therefore typically high kill ratios), the kills you would have to get to offset that CS is probably an obscene number.

Remember that the grade isn't comparing you to your team or the enemy, it's comparing you to every other Fizz score on the server (within the last month or so).
